article_title: Trump Victory Speech New Hampshire LIVE STREAM
article_text:
Donald Trump defeated his GOP rivals in New Hampshire tonight and will be delivering a victory speech to a large room of supporters shortly.

Trump had been expected to win New Hampshire for a while, and now the only question is how big a margin he ends up with.

Watch full speech above.
